    p.btext I pricked up my ears. It appeared that the hermit had lived by himself on this remote and tiny island for thirty years, and when opportunity occurred provisions were sent to him by kindly souls. He said that he was a Dane, but in the Torres Straits he was known as German Harry.

    br

    p
      span.btext His history went back a long way
      |
      |(его история началась очень давно;
      |
      span.f-coni to go back — возвращаться /на прежнее место/; брать начало
      |)
      span.btext . Thirty years before, he had been an able seaman on a sailing vessel that was wrecked
      |
      |(тридцать лет назад он был матросом на парусном судне, которое потерпело крушение;
      |
